---
title: Shrimp Jambalaya
description: This dish kicks off with the Cajun "Holy Trinity": celery, onion, and bell pepper. Rice ist cooked in a richt tomatoe sauce for the ultimate flavor bomb. We added juicy shrimp, but sausage or chicken would go equally well in this classic dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54beb1116ced6ea94d8b456b.jpg
